----------------------
| Common CSV Methods |
----------------------
_______________________________________________
| Method               | Description          |
| -------------------- | -------------------- |
| `csv.reader()`       | Read CSV             |
| `csv.writer()`       | Write CSV            |
| `writer.writerow()`  | Write one row        |
| `writer.writerows()` | Write multiple rows  |
| `csv.DictReader()`   | Read as dictionary   |
| `csv.DictWriter()`   | Write dictionaries   |
| `writeheader()`      | Write column headers |
-----------------------------------------------

Advantages
-----------
👉 Easy to store tabular data.
👉 Supported by Excel and Google Sheets.
👉 Easy to read and write.
👉 Lightweight file format.
👉 Good for data exchange.

Disadvantages
-------------
👉 Stores only plain text.
👉 No data types (everything is read as strings).
👉 Not suitable for complex or relational data.

